data.name: FontStrikeout
desc: These values are used to specify the kind of strikeout.
They may be expanded in future versions.

items.name: NONE
lines: specifies not to strike out the characters.

items.name: SINGLE
lines: specifies to strike out the characters with a single line.

items.name: DOUBLE
lines: specifies to strike out the characters with a double line.

items.name: DONTKNOW
lines: The strikeout mode is not specified.

items.name: BOLD
lines: specifies to strike out the characters with a bold line.

items.name: SLASH
lines: specifies to strike out the characters with slashes.

items.name: X
lines: specifies to strike out the characters with X's.
